title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jan 7 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jan 7 2022
description:
Can we trust the Supreme Court to strike down Biden's OSHA vax mandate? Shannon Bream of Fox News with Clay and Buck on the oral arguments today by the Supreme Court. She says of course covid is a serious issue that has taken many Americans, but some of what they were saying on the bench was "factually incorrect." The Yellowstone phenomenon. Clay: “It's basically a red state show that conquered the blue states.”
